WEBVTT

00:00:01.692 --> 00:00:05.707
So two weeks ago, I searched
the word "nationalist" on Twitter.

00:00:06.109 --> 00:00:07.950
The results were quite colorful,

00:00:07.974 --> 00:00:11.327
with expressions like,
"Emboldened Racist Moron," --

00:00:11.351 --> 00:00:12.361
(Laughter)

00:00:12.385 --> 00:00:14.510
"White Supremacist Idiot,"

00:00:14.534 --> 00:00:16.480
"Fascist Sock Puppets," --

00:00:16.504 --> 00:00:17.512
(Laughter)

00:00:17.536 --> 00:00:20.349
"Orwellian, Hitlerian, Terrifying."

00:00:20.373 --> 00:00:22.540
I then searched the word "globalist"

00:00:22.564 --> 00:00:25.766
and got things like,
"Socialist Sell-Outs,"

00:00:25.790 --> 00:00:28.750
"Disgusting Corporate Propaganda,"

00:00:28.774 --> 00:00:31.789
"Elitist Financial Overlords,"